<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Kotoblog</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- HTML5 Shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!-- WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file:// -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script>
    <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.3.0/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="headerphoto">
        <img src="/img/header_3.jpg" class="img-responsive" width="1000" height="350" />
    </div>
    {{ include('navbar.html.twig') }}
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
            <h2>Hello, world!!!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 hidden-xs hidden-sm">
            <h6><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-fire"></span> Подпишись на RSS и получай обновления блога!</h6>
            <h6><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-send"></span> Получать обновления по электронной почте:</h6>
            <form>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon">@</span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="E-mail">
                    <span class="input-group-btn">
                        <button class="btn btn-default" type="submit">OK</button>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </form>
            <h6><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-bullhorn"></span> Новое на блоге</h6>
            <h6><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star"></span> Еще популярные статьи</h6>
            <h6><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags"></span> Теги</h6>
            <h6><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share"></span> Ссылки</h6>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-9"><h6>© 2008 Котоблог</h6></div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <h6>Работает на <a target="_blank" href="http://silex.sensiolabs.org/" rel="nofollow">Silex</a></h6>
            <h6>Использует <a target="_blank" href="http://getbootstrap.com/" rel="nofollow">Twitter Bootstrap</a></h6>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
